---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Free AI Workshop for Business Owners | Leadership Growth Consulting"
  description="A free, practical workshop for established business owners who want to understand what AI can actually do for their business. No jargon, no hype. Just real solutions to real problems."
>
  <Nav />

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-white pt-28 pb-20 lg:pt-36 lg:pb-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-brand uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-semibold mb-6">Free Workshop</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-zinc-900 leading-tight mb-6 max-w-3xl">
        AI for business owners. No jargon, no hype. Just clarity.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-zinc-500 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
        A free, practical session to help you see what AI can actually do inside your business, and where to start.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHO IT'S FOR -->
  <section class="bg-stone-50 py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-zinc-900 mb-6">Who this is for</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            You've been running your business for a few years. It works. You've got a team, you've got clients, and things move forward.
          </p>
          <p>
            But AI keeps coming up. You hear about it constantly. And honestly, you're not sure where it fits, what's real, or where to even begin.
          </p>
          <p>
            That's exactly who this workshop is for. Business owners with 3 to 20 people who know their business inside out but want to understand what AI can genuinely help with, without the noise.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT YOU'LL LEARN -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-zinc-900 mb-4">What you'll walk away with</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-500 text-lg mb-14 max-w-2xl">
        This is business-first thinking with AI. Not AI for AI's sake.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-0 divide-y divide-zinc-100">
        <div class="py-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <p class="text-brand text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">01</p>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-zinc-900">Clarity on what AI actually is</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-2 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              We'll strip away the buzzwords and show you, in plain terms, what AI does well and where it falls short. No hype. Just an honest picture of what's possible right now.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="py-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <p class="text-brand text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">02</p>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-zinc-900">Real problems it can solve</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-2 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Following up on leads, onboarding clients more effectively, collecting documents, handling basic finance and admin tasks that nobody wants to do. These aren't big tech projects. They're small implementations that solve big headaches.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="py-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <p class="text-brand text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">03</p>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-zinc-900">A way to think about it</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-2 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              The biggest value isn't a specific tool. It's learning to look at your business and ask: what are the problems, the bottlenecks, the time sinks that AI could take off your plate? Once you can think that way, the opportunities become obvious.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="py-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <p class="text-brand text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">04</p>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-zinc-900">Making your people better, not replacing them</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-2 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              This isn't about cutting headcount. It's about giving your team the tools to be more effective in the roles they're already in. Less admin, less repetition, more time on the work that actually matters.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT THIS ISN'T -->
  <section class="bg-stone-50 py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-zinc-900 mb-6">What this isn't</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-zinc-600">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-zinc-300 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">-</span>It's not a tech course. You don't need to know how to code or build anything.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-zinc-300 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">-</span>It's not about wholesale digital transformation. No one's ripping up what works.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-zinc-300 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">-</span>It's not about replacing people. Full stop.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-zinc-300 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">-</span>It's not a sales pitch dressed up as a workshop. You'll leave with practical ideas whether we ever work together or not.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-zinc-900 mb-6">How it works</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            It's a free session. Interactive, practical, and built around your actual business.
          </p>
          <p>
            We'll look at where you're spending time that you shouldn't be, where your team is getting bogged down, and where AI could make an immediate difference. You'll leave with a clear picture of what's worth pursuing and what isn't.
          </p>
          <p>
            No preparation needed. Just bring an open mind and a willingness to think differently about how your business operates.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SIGN UP FORM -->
  <section class="bg-zinc-900 py-20 lg:py-28" id="signup">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl text-white mb-4">Apply for your free session</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Fill in a few details and we'll be in touch to get yours booked in.
        </p>
      </div>

      <form id="workshopForm" class="space-y-5">
        <div>
          <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-zinc-300 mb-1.5">Your name</label>
          <input
            type="text"
            id="name"
            name="name"
            required
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-brand-bright focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand-bright transition-colors"
            placeholder="Jane Smith"
          />
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-zinc-300 mb-1.5">Email address</label>
          <input
            type="email"
            id="email"
            name="email"
            required
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-brand-bright focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand-bright transition-colors"
            placeholder="jane@company.com"
          />
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="company" class="block text-sm font-medium text-zinc-300 mb-1.5">Company name</label>
          <input
            type="text"
            id="company"
            name="company"
            required
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-brand-bright focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand-bright transition-colors"
            placeholder="Acme Ltd"
          />
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="teamSize" class="block text-sm font-medium text-zinc-300 mb-1.5">Team size</label>
          <select
            id="teamSize"
            name="teamSize"
            required
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-700 rounded-lg text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-brand-bright focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand-bright transition-colors"
          >
            <option value="" disabled selected class="text-zinc-500">Select your team size</option>
            <option value="1-3">1-3 people</option>
            <option value="4-10">4-10 people</option>
            <option value="11-20">11-20 people</option>
            <option value="20+">20+ people</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <button
          type="submit"
          id="submitBtn"
          class="w-full bg-white text-zinc-900 px-8 py-4 font-medium hover:bg-zinc-100 transition-colors rounded-lg text-center mt-4"
        >
          Apply for your free session
        </button>

        <div id="formMessage" class="text-center text-sm mt-4 hidden"></div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<script>
  const form = document.getElementById('workshopForm') as HTMLFormElement;
  const submitBtn = document.getElementById('submitBtn') as HTMLButtonElement;
  const formMessage = document.getElementById('formMessage') as HTMLDivElement;

  form?.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    submitBtn.disabled = true;
    submitBtn.textContent = 'Submitting...';
    formMessage.classList.add('hidden');

    const data = {
      name: (document.getElementById('name') as HTMLInputElement).value.trim(),
      email: (document.getElementById('email') as HTMLInputElement).value.trim(),
      company: (document.getElementById('company') as HTMLInputElement).value.trim(),
      teamSize: (document.getElementById('teamSize') as HTMLSelectElement).value,
    };

    try {
      const res = await fetch('/api/workshop-signup', {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
        body: JSON.stringify(data),
      });

      if (res.ok) {
        form.innerHTML = `
          <div class="text-center py-8">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-white mb-3">You're in.</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-400">We'll be in touch shortly to get your session booked.</p>
          </div>
        `;
      } else {
        const err = await res.json().catch(() => ({}));
        formMessage.textContent = err.error || 'Something went wrong. Please try again.';
        formMessage.className = 'text-center text-sm mt-4 text-red-400';
        submitBtn.disabled = false;
        submitBtn.textContent = 'Apply for your free session';
      }
    } catch {
      formMessage.textContent = 'Something went wrong. Please try again.';
      formMessage.className = 'text-center text-sm mt-4 text-red-400';
      submitBtn.disabled = false;
      submitBtn.textContent = 'Apply for your free session';
    }
  });
</script>
